Question: The right image shows a connected bunch of exactly four bananas.

Reference Answer: False

Left image URL: http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Gx8CHBr6P6k/T04mawPgz9I/AAAAAAAAISs/QQXAJNe3zRo/s1600/nendran.jpg

Right image URL: http://www.yummytummyaarthi.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/1619661_10200777926525435_1424085238_n.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many bananas are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are the bananas connected?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are there exactly four bananas?')
ANSWER3=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 4 and {ANSWER1} and {ANSWER2}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER3)
```
